  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pancreatic exocrine insufficiency is known to impair nutrient absorption, especially fat, but
      few data exist about protein absorption. We aimed to investigate this question and assess the
      enzyme substitution efficiency using a sensitive method.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
